      "e.g. $3\\,248 \\div 4 = (3\\,200 \\div 4) + (48 \\div 4) = 800 + 12 = 812$.",
      "Choose parts that the divisor goes into without remainder where possible."
    ],
    "steps": [
      "Break the number into convenient place-value parts.",
      "Divide each part by the divisor.",
      "Add the part-quotients for the answer."
    ]
  },
